<br>
well anyway take heart that we will (supposedly) be seeing improved weapon drops.<br>
<br>
disclaimer: i cant remember where i read all that. and more to the point i cant remember if knights are going to be getting similarly improved weapon drops as well. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=eqduffy>EQDuffy</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 7<br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/4/03 9:05 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3247.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: take heart ...</span><hr size=1> Skill caps make a big difference.  Knights notice a 5% or so DPS from equiping the range item with a 5% bonus to 2HB skill (when using a 2HB of course).<br>
<br>
Not to mention every parse I've seen for similarly geared warriors/knights has shown that warriors consistently outdamage knights, with pure melee anyway.<br>
